<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="Technical services for retail POS systems, WordPress development, OpenCart stores, SuiteCRM customization, and business system integration in Dubai.">
  <title>Technical Services - Business Solutions | VistaDocs Center</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/img/identity.png">
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/img/identity.png">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  
  <%- include('partials/breadcrumbs') %>
  
  <main>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="page-title">Technical Services</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">Business system implementation and integration for SMEs</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="technical-services-section">
    <div class="container">
      
      <div class="service-category">
        <h2>Retail and Operations</h2>
        <div class="tech-services-grid">
          
          <article class="tech-service-card">
            <h3>POS System Setup</h3>
            <p>Installation and configuration for single-location retail stores and restaurants. Hardware connection, payment integration, product catalog setup.</p>
            <div class="service-meta">
              <span class="scope-tag">Single Location</span>
              <span class="scope-tag">Up to 10 Terminals</span>
            </div>
            <a href="/services/technical/pos-system-setup" class="btn btn-outline">View Service</a>
          </article>

        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-category">
        <h2>Web Development</h2>
        <div class="tech-services-grid">
          
          <article class="tech-service-card">
            <h3>WordPress Development</h3>
            <p>Custom theme development and plugin customization for business websites. Responsive design, content migration, basic WooCommerce setup.</p>
            <div class="service-meta">
              <span class="scope-tag">Custom Themes</span>
              <span class="scope-tag">Under 100k Visitors/Month</span>
            </div>
            <a href="/services/technical/wordpress-development" class="btn btn-outline">View Service</a>
          </article>

          <article class="tech-service-card">
            <h3>OpenCart Development</h3>
            <p>E-commerce store setup and custom module development. UAE payment gateway integration, product catalog management, shipping configuration.</p>
            <div class="service-meta">
              <span class="scope-tag">Single Store</span>
              <span class="scope-tag">Up to 50k Products</span>
            </div>
            <a href="/services/technical/opencart-development" class="btn btn-outline">View Service</a>
          </article>

          <article class="tech-service-card">
            <h3>Custom Web Application</h3>
            <p>Business workflow tools, client portals, and internal management systems. User authentication, database design, admin panels.</p>
            <div class="service-meta">
              <span class="scope-tag">Small Business</span>
              <span class="scope-tag">Up to 10k Users/Month</span>
            </div>
            <a href="/services/technical/custom-web-application" class="btn btn-outline">View Service</a>
          </article>

        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-category">
        <h2>Business Systems</h2>
        <div class="tech-services-grid">
          
          <article class="tech-service-card">
            <h3>SuiteCRM Customization</h3>
            <p>CRM configuration, workflow automation, and third-party integration. Custom fields, sales pipeline setup, email integration.</p>
            <div class="service-meta">
              <span class="scope-tag">Up to 50 Users</span>
              <span class="scope-tag">Workflow Automation</span>
            </div>
            <a href="/services/technical/suitecrm-customization" class="btn btn-outline">View Service</a>
          </article>

          <article class="tech-service-card">
            <h3>System Integration</h3>
            <p>Connect business systems via API. Data synchronization between e-commerce, CRM, accounting, and payment platforms.</p>
            <div class="service-meta">
              <span class="scope-tag">Up to 5 Systems</span>
              <span class="scope-tag">API-Based</span>
            </div>
            <a href="/services/technical/system-integration" class="btn btn-outline">View Service</a>
          </article>

        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="service-notice">
        <h2>Service Scope</h2>
        <p>All technical services are scoped for small business to SME operations. We do not support:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Enterprise deployments over 100 users</li>
          <li>Multi-location or franchise operations</li>
          <li>Real-time applications (websockets, live sync)</li>
          <li>Mobile native app development</li>
          <li>Legacy systems without API documentation</li>
          <li>Server infrastructure management or DevOps</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Contact us to confirm your project fits within supported scope before engaging.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
  </main>
  
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
